### Scheduler 定时任务 API 测试

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api/scheduler
@token = your_token_here

### 1. 创建新任务 - 带自定义参数
POST {{baseUrl}}/tasks
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "custom_task_with_params",
  "cron_spec": "0 */5 * * * *",
  "description": "每5分钟执行一次的自定义任务，带参数",
  "enabled": true,
  "task_type": "daily_log_output",
  "params": {
    "message": "这是从参数传入的自定义消息",
    "interval": 300,
    "retry_count": 3
  }
}

### 2. 创建碳月报汇总任务 - 指定年月参数
POST {{baseUrl}}/tasks
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "carbon_monthly_agg_custom",
  "cron_spec": "0 0 2 1 * *",
  "description": "每月2号凌晨2点执行碳月报汇总",
  "enabled": true,
  "task_type": "carbon_report_monthly_aggregation",
  "params": {
    "year": 2024,
    "month": 12
  }
}

### 3. 列出所有定时任务
GET {{baseUrl}}/tasks
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. 获取任务状态 - custom_task_with_params
GET {{baseUrl}}/tasks/custom_task_with_params
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5. 获取任务状态 - carbon_monthly_agg_custom
GET {{baseUrl}}/tasks/carbon_monthly_agg_custom
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6. 禁用任务 - custom_task_with_params
PUT {{baseUrl}}/tasks/custom_task_with_params/disable
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 7. 启用任务 - custom_task_with_params
PUT {{baseUrl}}/tasks/custom_task_with_params/enable
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 8. 删除任务 - custom_task_with_params
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/tasks/custom_task_with_params
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 9. 再次列出所有任务（验证删除）
GET {{baseUrl}}/tasks
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2. 获取任务状态 - example_every_minute
GET {{baseUrl}}/tasks/example_every_minute
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3. 获取任务状态 - example_daily_2am
GET {{baseUrl}}/tasks/example_daily_2am
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. 获取任务状态 - example_every_5min
GET {{baseUrl}}/tasks/example_every_5min
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5. 禁用任务 - example_every_minute
PUT {{baseUrl}}/tasks/example_every_minute/disable
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6. 启用任务 - example_every_5min
PUT {{baseUrl}}/tasks/example_every_5min/enable
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 7. 删除任务 - example_every_5min
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/tasks/example_every_5min
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 8. 再次列出所有任务（验证删除）
GET {{baseUrl}}/tasks
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
